transcript:

Executive: Hello sir, good morning.
Customer: Oh, good morning.
Executive: Uh, actually sir, Gaurav was trying to connect with you over the video meeting, sir. So what is the problem and discuss further things. 
Customer: Abhi thoda busy hai, main call karta hu sir.
Executive: Sir, aapka feedback tha uske regarding humne aapko details share kari thi sir. Your end date will remain same, right?
Executive: Abhi aur koi concern toh nahi hai apart from this?
Customer: Hello?
Customer: Uh, 3:00, 3:00 clock mein fix karo.
Executive: Actually kal bhi schedule tha. Are you available for 10 minutes, aap available hai abhi sir? We can discuss now. Not more than 10 minutes.
Customer: Ha, mere paas humne abhi customer padi hai.
Executive: Accha.
Executive: 3 baje abhi
